OL,3,CSaudi authorities say fourteen have
OL,4,Cbeen killed in oil company helicopter
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FAt least 14 people were killed in
OL,8,FSaudi Arabia when a helicopter
OL,9,Fcarrying them crashed on Sunday,
OL,10,Fkilling everyone aboard, according to
OL,11,Fthe Saudi Ministry of Energy.
OL,13,FThe accident occurred around 6 am
OL,14,Flocal time, and all of the people
OL,15,Fkilled were Saudi nationals, the
OL,16,Fstatement said. There was no further
OL,17,Finformation about what caused the
OL,18,Fcrash.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/2
