OL,3,CSaudi authorities say fourteen have
OL,4,Cbeen killed in oil company helicopter
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FThe helicopter belonged to Aramco, the
OL,8,Fworld's largest oil company, which is
OL,9,Fmajority-owned by Saudi Arabia.
OL,11,FThis is a breaking news story, more
OL,12,Finformation to follow.
